Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:02.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We face another attack from{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the legendary Seven Spectres.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's their connection\nwith Kohaku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango's lost brother who is\nbeing controlled by Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....so{\i0} Kyokotsu died?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master Jakotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}well....{\i0}\NCan't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was the weakest one\namong us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:19.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:26.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Inuyasha handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:30.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please ascertain that\nfor yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} I can't wait\nto see you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what color your blood is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think so. I didn't sense\nanything like that around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're going\nto subdue something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:25.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So pretentious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We had such a scare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hear ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was a lesson from Buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have seen the fear\nin your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm.... However....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a mountain shrine over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Talk about heaven in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is heaven sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You always try to depend\non {\i1}others....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your weak heart is why\nyou see illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, let us seek shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You intend to depend\non others, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that the border patrol\nwas totally annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was terrible, I hear.\NNo way man could've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are the rumors true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That phantoms of the Band of Seven\nmound have been resurrected?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Phantoms of the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:01.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....may{\i0} I inquire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're gonna ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't just pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:12.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Seven-Man Mound was a\nmound to quiet the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over a decade {\i1}ago....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They came here from\nthe eastern province.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were seven mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They served no lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But worked from war to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they were so {\i1}strong....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They could do the work\nof a hundred men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But their killing style\nwas too atrocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those who were slain\nby the seven mercenaries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,were cut up, {\i1}burned....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were a group of evil men\nwho loved to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the warlords who\nfeared their {\i1}strength....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,sold them out and ordered\nthem hunted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard they put up\na hard fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The seven mercenaries\nescaped into the {\i1}mountains....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there were totally outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And just a bit further north,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they were finally captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Each one was beheaded\nand buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, the villagers feared\ntheir curse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and decided to quiet\nthe seven souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And erected a mound\nat the base of the sacred mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is the Seven-Man Mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We heard that those spirits\nhave been resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's said that the mound\nbroke apart into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there wasn't any lightning, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's believed that\nthe seven souls escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm....dead souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's possible that with\NNaraku's evil gone from {\i1}here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:10.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all the rabble have become free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Specters or {\i1}demons....{\i0} I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we're just walking\nin that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we come across them,\nwe just kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:34.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sensed Kohaku's presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be somewhere\nin this mountain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saimyosho....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to erase it...\nbut it wouldn't go away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That face...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:37.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're still under Naraku's {\i1}spell....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why is your {\i1}face....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just remember a little at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be together from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were late, so I came instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}woman....you{\i0} know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make way in the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?\NYou look strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're going on ahead,\nbe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:55.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hear a frightening\nspecter appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're on our way to\nexterminate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you have no idea\nwhat it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm that....specter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gun battalion! To the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A specter over a decade old\nwouldn't be familiar with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What were those sounds just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe....gunfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is the matchlock guns\NI heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:13.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Second battalion! To the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:30.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:37.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The smell of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....and{\i0} lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He just swung his {\i1}sword....{\i0}\nfrom that distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This brings back memories\nof the {\i1}past....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Do not fear him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Surround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's using hypnotic magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't use such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither then nor now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This smell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's weak, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of graveyard soil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is unusual. I'll take it\nback to Brother Renkotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the warriors from\nthe crossroads earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were slain by that one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could you be....Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'd you know my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I love those ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give 'em to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't smell like\na living person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just of dead bodies\nand graveyard soil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:38.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, could he {\i1}be....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers were talking\nabout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That some disgusting specter\nappeared from his grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A group of seven evil men\nwho loved to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mercenaries who were later\nhunted down and beheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be one of the seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're pretty sexy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I suck him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has a Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he revived through the\npower of the shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who gave you the\NSacred Jewel shard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I love that angry face, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:46.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make you talk\nabout everything you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting sword you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sword or yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back! It's a trick sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heh-heh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it was strange...\nthe way the soldiers were slain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:39.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were all downed in one blow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without any time to repel him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I figured it would be\nsomething tricky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But not only that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His sword is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a bending sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the Snake Sword\nof Master Jakotsu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if he repels it,\nit comes right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sword....it's like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I can't tell where\nthe sword will appear next!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good....{\i0} That face turns me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Show more fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?\NInuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woman....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't interfere, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay out of my fun\nwith Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who gave you the\NSacred Jewel shard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Confess now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Are you all right?!\N- Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just a graze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the Sacred Jewel shard was\nprobably from Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Earlier, when you sensed the Sacred {\i1}Jewel....{\i0}\nit was Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Near Kohaku, I saw the saimyosho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he's still under\NNaraku's spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah....he's at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, the poison has paralyzed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What could he want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a poison barrier\nall around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one will come to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so {\i1}blessed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To have such a\ncute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:02.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not perfect, but\nplease accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:04.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:09.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Stealthy Poison Master: Mukotsu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru?\NWhat're you doing here?!
